<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Paulus Imhoff</head><p>Der Rat lädt Imhoff binnen vier Wochen vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_338" id="168v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_338_r1l1">Paulus Jm Hof </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_338_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Paulus VVir heiſʒen dich vnd gepieten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l3">dir auch beẏ deinem eyde daʒ du nicht laſʒeſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l5">du kumſt in den nehſten vıer <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l6">ſant Michelstag ſchıerſt herheim cʒu vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l8"> <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etwaʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"> gar </del> nötlichs 
<add><ab facs="#facs_338_line_1576487220955_4703">
<del rend="strikethrough">ın geheim </del></ab></add> mit dır cʒu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l9"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als du <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> vvirdeſt / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_338_r1l10"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mıchaelis Anno <expan>vndecı<ex>m</ex>o</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_338" id="168v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Paulus im Hof </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Paulus, wir heiszen dich und gepieten dir
                        auch bey deinem eyde, daz du nicht laszest, du kumst in den nehsten vier
                            <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nach <app><note><q type="date">sant Michelstag schierst</q>29.09.1411</note></app> herheim
                        czu uns, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etwaz nötlichs mit dir czu
                                <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als du <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wirdest.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Michaelis anno
                                <expan>undeci<ex>m</ex>o</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
